&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;b5.&lt;/b&gt; glosses Skt. &lt;i&gt;methaken=&lt;/i&gt; (instr.sg.) 'bad deed' ([[SHT VII]]: 142). Also for this gloss, the facsimile in [[SHT V]] (plate 7) is indispensable.&lt;/p&gt;</item>
